summary:
Hi, I'm Shannen, and I’ve been lucky enough to have run projects for FMCG giants across the world to create elegant and effective branding and design solutions to their business challenges.

Specialties: brand & creative strategy, packaging design, POS & retail activation.

My goal is to use my experience to focus further on brand strategy.

On the side, I am also into calisthenics, art & photography, and a bit of DJing.
